rial election|2018]]}}\n{{s-inc|recent}}\n|-\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Deval Patrick]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Governor of Massachusetts]]|years=2015\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n|-\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|rows=2|before=[[Mike Pence]]|as=[[Vice President of the United States|Vice President]]}}\n{{s-ttl|rows=2|title=[[United States order of precedence|Order of Precedence of the United States]]|years=Within Massachusetts}}\n{{s-aft|after=Mayor of city<br>in which event is held}}\n|-\n{{s-aft|after=Otherwise {{Incumbent U.S. House Speaker}}<br>{{nowrap|''as [[Speaker of the United States House of Representatives|Speaker of the U.S. House of Representatives]]''}}}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Ned Lamont]]|as=[[Governor of Connecticut]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[United States order of precedence|Order of Precedence of the United States]]|years=Outside Massachusetts}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Larry Hogan]]|as=[[Governor of Maryland]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Charlie Baker cabinet}}\n{{Governors of Massachusetts}}\n{{Current Massachusetts statewide political officials}}\n{{Current U.S. governors}}\n{{Portal bar|Politics|United States}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Baker, Charlie}}\n[[Category:1956 births]]\n[[Category:20th-century American businesspeople]]\n[[Category:21st-century American businesspeople]]\n[[Category:21st-century American politicians]]\n[[Category:American corporate directors]]\n[[Category:American health care chief executives]]\n[[Category:American nonprofit chief executives]]\n[[Category:American people of English descent]]\n[[Category:Businesspeople from Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Candidates in the 2010 United States elections]]\n[[Category:Governors of Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Harvard College alumni]]\n[[Category:Kellogg School of Management alumni]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Massachusetts local politicians]]\n[[Category:Massachusetts Republicans]]\n[[Category:Massachusetts Secretaries of Administration and Finance]]\n[[Category:Massachusetts Secretarie